  <thing id="ioUmFeaKno" name="Fearful Knocker" description="{b}Description{/b}\nThis heavy metallic disk is carved in fanciful or frightful likeness of a humanoid or monstrous face, with a heavy ring in its mouth. If attached to a door, it seals the door with an {i}arcane lock{/i} and wards it with a {i}phantom trap{/i}. The {i}fearful knocker{/i} opens and closes the door by a command word. A creature touching the door without speaking the command word is affected as {i}scare{/i} (DC 13 Will partial). The {i}fearful knocker{/i} cannot be removed from the door except by the command word, destroying the door, or temporarily negating its power with {i}dispel magic{/i}." compset="Wondrous" summary="This heavy metallic disk is carved in fanciful or frightful likeness of a humanoid or monstrous face, with a heavy ring in its mouth.">
