  <thing id="ioUmMesMas" name="Mesmeric Mask" description="{b}Description{/b}\nThis transparent mask clings to the wearer&apos;s face, almost imperceptible to inspection (Perception DC 30) or magical examination (DC 30 caster level check to detect its presence). The wearer is immune to {i}charm{/i} and {i}dominate{/i} effects but is immediately aware of them and their source. As an immediate action when targeted with such an effect, the wearer may attempt to deceive the creature using the {i}charm{/i} or {i}dominate{/i} effect into believing it has succeeded (DC 20 Will save negates). If the save is failed, the mask-wearer gains a +20 bonus to Bluff or Perform (acting) skill checks to perpetuate the ruse that they are mentally controlled, and he may choose to accept the telepathic bond that accompanies a {i}dominate{/i} effect." compset="Wondrous" summary="This transparent mask clings to the wearer&apos;s face, almost imperceptible to inspection (Perception DC 30) or magical examination (DC 30 caster level check to detect its presence).">
