  <thing id="ioUmTenVes" name="Tentacle Vest" description="{b}Description{/b}\nThis leather vest is fringed with dangling strips. When the vest is worn, these strips become engorged, rubbery tentacles that squirm, lash, and twine. The {i}tentacle vest{/i} does not interfere with the wearer&apos;s actions and grant a +2 bonus to Climb and Swim checks, as well as to CMB for disarm, drag, grapple, and steal maneuvers. The {i}tentacle vest{/i} can be used to hold (but not wear or wield) one item as if it were in your hand. The tentacles cannot draw or sheathe a weapon nor retrieve or or stow an item in a character&apos;s pack; however, transferring an item from hand to {i}tentacle vest{/i} (or vice versa) is a swift action.\n\n{b}Note:{/b} +2 for Drag and Steal have not been implemented." compset="Wondrous" summary="This leather vest is fringed with dangling strips.">
