  <thing id="ioUmWitSty" name="Witchblood Stylus" description="{b}Description{/b}\nThis sharpened bone writing implement can be used by a witch to enhance the power of certain magical writings by infusing the blood of her familiar. If used to scribe a scroll of a patron spell, the scroll&apos;s save DC is set by the witch&apos;s actual Intelligence modifier, rather than the default minimum. A {i}glyph of warding{/i}, {i}symbol{/i}, or similar magical rune inscribed with a {i}witchblood stylus{/i} requires those triggering it to save twice; a creature failing either save suffers the full effects of the glyph, symbol, or rune. A {i}witchblood stylus{/i} may be used once per day, and using it inflicts 1 point of Constitution damage to the familiar per level of the spell being inscribed." compset="Wondrous" summary="This sharpened bone writing implement can be used by a witch to enhance the power of certain magical writings by infusing the blood of her familiar.">
