  <thing id="abUmStaSou" name="Stalwart Soul" description="The wielder of Grinning Skull receives a +4 morale bonus on attack rolls made to confirm critical hits against undead. This does not stack with Critical Focus. The wielder also receives this bonus on saves against any fear effect or spell cast by an undead creature. The wielder is also granted a save to negate such effects even if one is not normally allowed." compset="Ability" summary="The wielder of Grinning Skull receives a +4 morale bonus on attack rolls made to confirm critical hits against undead.">
