  <thing id="abUmVoidwr" name="Voidwrought" description="Voidwrought weapons are instilled with the darkness of space. As such, their blades appear night-black, and they do not reflect any light; rather, they seem to absorb light. Voidwrought weapons grant wielders a +1 insight bonus on their attack and damage rolls and the ability to see in normal darkness and magical darkness to a distance of 60 ft. (if a wielder already has this ability, the ranges in darkness are doubled)." compset="Ability">
