  <thing id="abUmNoWSoW" name="North Wind/South Wind" description="Once per day the wielder of spear of the four winds can call upon the blistering heat of the desert simoom or the frigid cold of the polar gale. He can cast {i}sirocco{/i} as a spell-like ability once per day. At the time of casting the wielder determines which wind he calls upon. A south wind deals fire damage as normal in the spell description. A north wind deals cold damage instead." compset="Ability">
