  <thing id="abUmDeflec" name="Deflecting" description="Once per round as an attack of opportunity you can deflect any ray aimed at you or anyone within your reach to another target by making a successful combat maneuver check. A failure results in you automatically being hit by the ray. The range of the spell remains unchanged." compset="Ability">
